in buildings such as penal institutions or special needs housing,
or anywhere an ordinary pull station would be operated for
reasons other than its intended purpose. The RMS-1T-KO station

The RMS-1T-KO has one Single Pole Normally Open contact rated
for 10 amps at 125 Vdc. It features terminal connectors for easy
field wiring. The key can be removed in both the “ON” and “OFF”
The RMS-1T-KO Station flush mounts to any standard North
